    <h1>Learn React.js</h1>
    <p>React.js is a JavaScript library used for building user interfaces, especially for single-page applications.</p>
    
    <h2>Why Learn React?</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Component-Based Architecture</li>
        <li>Fast Rendering with Virtual DOM</li>
        <li>Strong Community Support</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Steps to Get Started</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Install Node.js and npm</li>
        <li>Create a React App using Create React App</li>
        <li>Understand JSX and Components</li>
        <li>Learn State and Props</li>
        <li>Build and Deploy Your First App</li>
    </ol>
